

HTML boilerplate: ----------------------! + TAB 
Open the palette to search for a file:--Ctrl + P 
Add cursors to all matching selections:-Ctrl + Shift + L 
Undo:  ---------------------------------Ctrl + U 
Select Current Line: ------------------Ctrl + L 
Zen Mode: -----------------------------Ctrl + K Z 
Toggle Sidebar:------------------------Ctrl + B 
Search Global Files:-------------------Ctrl + Shift + F 
Search on file:------------------------Ctrl + F 
Find and Replace:----------------------Ctrl + H 
Delete the previous Word:--------------Ctrl + Backspace 
Move line up/Down:---------------------Alt + up/down arrow 
Add multiple cursors:------------------Ctrl + Alt +up/down arrow
Comment Line:--------------------------Ctrl + / 
Comment Line:-------------------------Ctrl + K + Ctrl + C 
Split View:---------------------------Ctrl + \ 
Switch Between views:-----------------Ctrl +1, Ctrl + 2 .. 
Duplicate Line:-----------------------Alt + Shift + up/down 
Navigate to a specific line:----------Ctrl + g 
Open Terminal:------------------------Ctrl + ` 
To Close a TAB:-----------------------Ctrl + W 
To Close all TAB:---------------------Ctrl + Shift + W 



